	(text "Defaults to flash boot (HIGH)\nWhen active (LOW): USB device\n\nThis pulls on the RP2040 flash\nSS line. Purposefully *not* \ndebounced, as we have on the\norder of 10us for a stable \nstate on boot.  So either\nhold down + power-up, or \nhave a stiff pull with no\nRC filter in the loop."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 38.735 128.905 0)
