	(text "Stronger pull-downs on carrier side \nallow us to determine if an ASIC board \nis actually connected (vs and FPGA sim \nboard, or nothing).\nOn startup, read the ctrl en and reset, \nif they are low, we have an ASIC carrier.  \nFrom then, drive the lines normally."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
